WEBVTT


00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:01.880
5 things that men love,

00:00:01.881 --> 00:00:03.801
but they will never admit to you.

00:00:03.802 --> 00:00:07.561
Number one: when you run up to them with excitement and hug them!

00:00:07.562 --> 00:00:09.001
if you haven't seen them all day,

00:00:09.002 --> 00:00:10.741
or maybe even have seen them,

00:00:10.840 --> 00:00:13.580
but men love to see you get excited for them!

00:00:13.640 --> 00:00:17.120
they feel like a man when they can pick you up and embrace you!

00:00:17.121 --> 00:00:21.541
number two: whenever you kiss their head / kiss their cheek

00:00:21.560 --> 00:00:22.520
men love this!

00:00:22.521 --> 00:00:25.941
okay they love affection and they love to feel special

00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:27.120
number three

00:00:27.121 --> 00:00:29.021
when you wear his clothes.

00:00:29.400 --> 00:00:31.840
men love when you wear their baggy T-shirt,

00:00:31.841 --> 00:00:33.041
hoodie, or shorts!

00:00:33.042 --> 00:00:34.581
they think it's precious.

00:00:34.840 --> 00:00:35.640
not only that,

00:00:35.641 --> 00:00:38.681
they think that you wanna feel closer to them by wearing their clothes

00:00:38.682 --> 00:00:42.921
and it's true! We love to smell their hoodies or shirts that smell like them

00:00:42.922 --> 00:00:47.001
Number four: telling them where you actually want to eat okay

00:00:47.002 --> 00:00:48.101
men love this!

00:00:48.120 --> 00:00:50.920
be honest tell them where you actually want to eat,

00:00:50.921 --> 00:00:53.961
instead of turning down every option that he gives you

00:00:53.962 --> 00:00:56.921
and then you end up going to the place that you wanted to originally

00:00:56.922 --> 00:00:57.841
just be honest

00:00:57.842 --> 00:00:59.101
tell them where you wanna eat

00:00:59.280 --> 00:01:01.160
men love when you know what you want!

00:01:01.161 --> 00:01:05.021
No. 5 playing with their hair or giving them back scratches

00:01:05.080 --> 00:01:06.560
men love this

00:01:06.561 --> 00:01:08.401
they're not used to pampering themselves,

00:01:08.402 --> 00:01:10.801
the only person who touches them is probably you

00:01:10.802 --> 00:01:14.241
so whenever you play with their hair or scratch their back

00:01:14.242 --> 00:01:16.521
they feel like a happy golden retriever

00:01:16.522 --> 00:01:17.201
they love it

00:01:17.202 --> 00:01:18.281
and they die for it!

00:01:18.282 --> 00:01:19.841
Men love all of these things

00:01:19.842 --> 00:01:21.741
